{"tid":1482829,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【8.18】【民陣發表大會宣言】","createTime":"2019-08-18T08:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T08:52:10.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f00bb5020227d9d4b23f892d042099c98195e96","tid":1482829,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"-<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重申特區政府必須實質回應反送中運動的五大訴求</strong></span><br />\n-止黑暴、制警亂，停止一切濫權濫暴行動<br />\n-要求保安局局長李家超、警務處處長盧偉聰、行動處處長鄧炳強和新任副處長劉業成問責下台<br />\n-6月12日至今警方失誤，高層責無旁貸，<span style=\"color: red;\">需要從根本改變警隊</span><br />\n-反送中運動的初心，<span style=\"color: red;\">是守護香港人享有的法治和自由</span>，免於中國式政法制度和政治暴力的恐懼<br />\n-無論是前線的抗爭者或屋邨街坊，兩個月來歷盡警隊以催淚彈、布袋彈和橡膠子彈<span style=\"color: red;\">清場和圍捕的暴力</span>，甚至是<span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會無差別的襲擊</span><br />\n-警察的暴力不只傷害人身，甚至是製造<span style=\"color: red;\">非人化的恐懼環境</span>。香港在國際社會的文明形象，<span style=\"color: red;\">正被警察逐步破壞</span>。<br />\n-警方變成<span style=\"color: red;\">管治機器</span>，在高處施放催淚彈、近距離射擊抗爭者，超出人性可以接受範圍，<span style=\"color: red;\">超出國際人權標準</span>，強調不是針對警察，而是針對警察<span style=\"color: red;\">違法暴力、黑社會以及警黑勾結</span>。<br />\n-<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8.31會有活動 詳情有待公佈</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475334-20190818.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475334-20190818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=7b3cded0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475334-20190818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e5f2a911\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475334-20190818.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2223542/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2223542%2F&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPKwvV4D0j